original: Ekelöf, Carl Thore Eberhard, komminister, Skövde, f. 30/11/02 i Gbg. G. 30 m. Margareta Ternstedt. Barn: Hermain f. 3’1, Elisabeth 32, Lans 38. — Stud:ex. i Gbg 21, teol. fil. ex. 23, teol. kand. .samt prakt. teol. prov 26, prästv. f. Skara stift 27. V. pastor i Hjo o. Fägre 27, v. kommin. i Fröje-red 28, kommin. där 29, kommin. i Skövde fr. 37, mil :pastor.
translated: Ekelöf, Carl Thore Eberhard, vicar, Skövde, b. 30/11/02 in Gothenburg. Married in 1930 to Margareta Ternstedt. Children: Hermain b. 1931, Elisabeth b. 1932, Lans b. 1938. — Completed his high school studies in Gothenburg in 1921, theology degree in 1923, theology practical exam in 1926, ordained as a priest in Skara diocese in 1927. Worked as assistant pastor in Hjo and Fägre in 1927, assistant vicar in Fröja-Red in 1928, vicar there in 1929, vicar in Skövde from 1937, military pastor.
